OL,3,CConstructing in the cold: Inside the
OL,4,Cbold build at the bottom of the world
OL,6,FIf the producers of Grand Designs were
OL,7,Flooking for the most extreme building
OL,8,Fproject ever, I think I've found it.
OL,9,F67 degrees south, deep in the
OL,10,FAntarctic Circle.
OL,12,FOn Ryder Bay, 1,000 miles from the
OL,13,Fnearest city, is the British Antarctic
OL,14,FSurvey's Rothera Research Station.
OL,16,FFor 50 years, scientists, engineers,
OL,17,Fand adventurers have been based here,
OL,18,Fbraving conditions as cold as -20C
OL,19,Fand permanent darkness during the
OL,20,Fpolar winter.
