OL,3,CConstructing in the cold: Inside the
OL,4,Cbold build at the bottom of the world
OL,6,FFor the past six years, builders have
OL,7,Fbeen here too, constructing the
OL,8,FDiscovery Building.
OL,10,FIt's a 90-meter-long, 4,500 m
OL,11,Ffacility that serves as an office,
OL,12,Fstoreroom, power plant, hospital,
OL,13,Fcontrol tower, and nerve centre of
OL,14,FBritain's Antarctic operations.
OL,16,FThere isn't a Screwfix or B&Q nearby,
OL,17,Fso every single tool, tile, and tin of
OL,18,Fpaint has had to be shipped in ` 400
OL,19,Fcontainers in total.
