OL,3,CConstructing in the cold: Inside the
OL,4,Cbold build at the bottom of the world
OL,6,FSurprisingly, fire is a huge risk
OL,7,Fhere. Antarctica is so dry that it's
OL,8,Ftechnically a desert. With no prospect
OL,9,Fof a quick rescue during the winter,
OL,10,Fthey can't take any risks.
OL,12,FA massive 40,000-litre tank of water
OL,13,Fcan be emptied onto flames in just 30
OL,14,Fminutes.
OL,16,FAll water is desalinated from the sea.
OL,17,F"Why don't you just melt the snow?", I
OL,18,Fasked plumber Tobias.
