OL,3,CConstructing in the cold: Inside the
OL,4,Cbold build at the bottom of the world
OL,6,F"Back in the day, about 30 or 40 years
OL,7,Fago, they did, but they only had one
OL,8,Fshower per week. Today, with these
OL,9,Fsystems, we can produce 10,000 litres
OL,10,Fof water a day."
OL,12,FThe colour scheme has raised a few
OL,13,Feyebrows. Stairwells and offices are
OL,14,Fpainted in bold floor-to-ceiling blue,
OL,15,Fgreen, red, or yellow.
OL,17,FIt's the architect's attempt to
OL,18,Fcounteract the dull, dark winter
OL,19,Fnights, but I get the sense that some
OL,20,Fof the scientists might prefer a more
OL,21,Fmuted magnolia.
