OL,3,CConstructing in the cold: Inside the
OL,4,Cbold build at the bottom of the world
OL,6,FThe project has cost #100 million of
OL,7,Ftaxpayers' money. It's a symbol of the
OL,8,FUK's commitment to polar science`not
OL,9,Fto mention the geopolitical importance
OL,10,Fof maintaining a physical presence on
OL,11,Fthe continent.
OL,13,FThere's plenty of snagging to do over
OL,14,Fwinter. Then the not insignificant
OL,15,Fchallenge of dismantling the old
OL,16,Fbuildings it has replaced.
